name: Neeko Style
description:
This is a really cool Textual Inversion inspired by my League of Legends main - Neeko! It's not meant to reproduce her likeness 100% - I've always been drawn to her aesthetic; the nature theme and the awesome color palette, and I wanted to replicate some of that in my images - but not necessarily insert her likeness (unless I wanted to). This embedding can do that (see example pics!)

If you'd like the effect to come through stronger (some models need it), try bumping up the emphasis on Style-Neeko - see the images below. Mostly, you'll need to reduce the strength of Neeko - it comes through pretty strongly.

Please consider joining my Patreon! Advanced SD tutorials, settings explanations, adult-art, from a female content creator (me!) patreon.com/theally
